# Build context for Dockerfile.crm — keep only what cabal needs: the .cabal/project files,
# the hand-written FFI (hs/) and the generated MAlonzo Haskell (_build/MAlonzo). Everything
# else (Agda sources, the JS build, the NixOS dist-newstyle, docs) is excluded to keep the
# context small and the build hermetic.
.git
dist-newstyle
node_modules
package.json
package-lock.json
src
examples
examples_html
doc
docs
test
runtime
benchmark
scripts
debug-*.md
*.md
_crmbin
Dockerfile.crm
# within _build: drop the JS backend output and the Agda interface cache, keep MAlonzo/
_build/jAgda.*
_build/2.9.0
**/*.agdai
